title.en: Contribution from four branches in the Arfon district of Merched y Wawr towards the project on Welsh place names.
title.cy: Cyfraniad pedair cangen o Ranbarth Arfon o Ferched y Wawr i'r proiect ar gasglu enwau lleoedd Cymraeg.

description.en: Information on work collected by the branches of Brynaearau, Llandwrog, Deiniolen and Bangor of Merched y Wawr. It contains lists of field names.
description.cy: Gwybodaeth am waith canghennau Brynaerau,Llandwrog, Deiniolen a Bangor o Ferched y Wawr. Mae'n cynnwys rhestr o enwau caeau.
